```mermaid
%% Animation States and Transitions Workflow
stateDiagram-v2
    %% FAQ Page Entry Animations
    [*] --> PageLoad: User visits FAQ
    PageLoad --> HeroAnimation: Initialize hero section
    HeroAnimation --> SearchBarAnimation: Animate search bar
    SearchBarAnimation --> CategoryGridAnimation: Stagger category cards
    CategoryGridAnimation --> SidebarAnimation: Slide in sidebar
    SidebarAnimation --> PageReady: All animations complete
    
    %% Search Interaction States
    PageReady --> SearchFocus: User clicks search
    SearchFocus --> SearchTyping: User starts typing
    SearchTyping --> SearchSuggestions: Show suggestions dropdown
    SearchSuggestions --> SearchResults: Display results
    SearchResults --> SearchBlur: User clicks away
    SearchBlur --> PageReady: Return to ready state
    
    %% FAQ Accordion States
    PageReady --> FAQClosed: Default FAQ state
    FAQClosed --> FAQExpanding: User clicks FAQ
    FAQExpanding --> FAQOpen: Animation complete
    FAQOpen --> FAQClosing: User clicks again
    FAQClosing --> FAQClosed: Animation complete
    
    %% FAQ Hover States (Desktop)
    FAQClosed --> FAQHover: Mouse enters
    FAQHover --> FAQClosed: Mouse leaves
    FAQOpen --> FAQOpenHover: Mouse enters open FAQ
    FAQOpenHover --> FAQOpen: Mouse leaves
    
    %% Category Selection States
    PageReady --> CategoryGrid: Default categories
    CategoryGrid --> CategoryHover: Mouse over category
    CategoryHover --> CategoryGrid: Mouse leave
    CategoryGrid --> CategorySelected: User clicks category
    CategorySelected --> CategoryFiltered: Apply filter animation
    CategoryFiltered --> PageReady: Filter complete
    
    %% Sidebar States
    PageReady --> SidebarVisible: Desktop default
    SidebarVisible --> SidebarHidden: Mobile responsive
    SidebarHidden --> SidebarSlideIn: Mobile menu button
    SidebarSlideIn --> SidebarOverlay: Overlay active
    SidebarOverlay --> SidebarSlideOut: Close button/backdrop
    SidebarSlideOut --> SidebarHidden: Animation complete
    
    %% Feedback Animation States
    FAQOpen --> FeedbackIdle: Feedback buttons visible
    FeedbackIdle --> FeedbackThumbsUp: User clicks positive
    FeedbackThumbsUp --> FeedbackThanks: Show thank you animation
    FeedbackThanks --> FeedbackComplete: Animation done
    
    FeedbackIdle --> FeedbackThumbsDown: User clicks negative
    FeedbackThumbsDown --> FeedbackForm: Slide down form
    FeedbackForm --> FeedbackSubmitting: User submits
    FeedbackSubmitting --> FeedbackSuccess: Show success animation
    FeedbackSuccess --> FeedbackComplete: Animation done
    
    %% Error and Loading States
    SearchTyping --> SearchError: Search fails
    SearchError --> SearchTyping: User retries
    
    PageLoad --> LoadingError: Page load fails
    LoadingError --> PageLoad: User refreshes
    
    %% CTA Button States
    PageReady --> CTADefault: CTA buttons visible
    CTADefault --> CTAHover: Mouse over CTA
    CTAHover --> CTADefault: Mouse leave
    CTADefault --> CTAPressed: User clicks CTA
    CTAPressed --> CTARedirect: Navigate to target
    
    %% Mobile Touch States
    FAQClosed --> FAQTouch: Touch start
    FAQTouch --> FAQExpanding: Touch end
    CategoryGrid --> CategoryTouch: Touch category
    CategoryTouch --> CategorySelected: Touch end
    
    %% Return to Ready State
    FeedbackComplete --> PageReady: Reset to ready
    CategoryFiltered --> PageReady: Category view ready
    CTARedirect --> [*]: User leaves page
    
    %% State Annotations
    note right of PageLoad
        Staggered entrance animations
        Duration: 1.2s total
    end note
    
    note right of FAQExpanding
        Smooth height transition
        Duration: 400ms cubic-bezier
    end note
    
    note right of SearchSuggestions
        Fade in with scale animation
        Duration: 200ms ease-out
    end note
    
    note right of SidebarSlideIn
        Transform translateX animation
        Duration: 300ms ease-out
    end note
    
    note right of FeedbackSuccess
        Bounce animation with color change
        Duration: 600ms ease-out
    end note
